<i>adverb</i>: 황홀히 [황홀히] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>황홀히 [황홀히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. magnificently; splendidly; brilliantly</dd><br>
<dd>눈이 부셔 흐릿하게 보일 정도로 아름답고 화려하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state of looking dazzlingly beautiful and splendid.</dd><br>
<dd>2. ecstatically; in a state of rapture</dd><br>
<dd>마음이나 시선을 빼앗겨 흥분된 상태로.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state of excitement from something catching the eye or stealing the heart.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>